   "source": [
    "#  Consensus-Based Ensemble Clustering for Customer Segmentation\n",
    "\n",
    "**Objective:** Apply multiple clustering algorithms (K-Means, Agglomerative, DBSCAN), combine their results using a Co-Association Matrix, and compare ensemble performance against individual methods.\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
